			"value": "<p><em>You control the ambient noise in the air, preventing the targets of your spells and songs from making any sound.</em></p><p><strong>No Action Cost</strong></p><p><em>Trigger: A creature fails their save against your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.MfhfSzLQbJqLCZ6q]{Blasting Volume} feature or a spell of yours of 1st level or higher that deals &amp;reference[psychic] or &amp;reference[thunder] damage.</em></p><ul><li><p>The creature is additionally &amp;reference[silenced] until the end of your next turn.</p></li></ul>",
